<br>
Your options here:<br>
<br>
Your personal photo.  Provide a link (URL) to a picture that you want to have appear on the left under your name. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The picture should be stored on your own site or on a site where you have permission to direct link.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  The Ape Vine uses the 60x60 limit, so if your pic is bigger, the system will compress it to fit and my distort it.  Other boards do not use the limt.  If you want to hide your pic, check the box marked private. You can also elect to hide your photo on individual posts, by unchecking the appropriate box under posting options.  <br>
<br>
Your name and birthdate.  If you want to hide all or part of this info, just check the private box.<br>
<br>
You may also provide as much or as little info on location and occupation as you wish.<br>
<br>
There are boxes for your hobbies and a brief personal bio.  This is optional.  <br>
<br>
ezSupporters can use html in your profile, non supporters must use ezcodes<br>
<br>
Contact info<br>
<br>
