<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Browsing and viewing</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
View only new topics<br>
Turning this feature on will show ONLY those topics that have new messages. When off, all topics are shown. It is suggested you turn this feature on once you get accustomed to using the forums. You can also toggle this option from the forum screens.  (I have this off)<br>
<br>
Move updated topics to top<br>
Checking this box will move updated topics to the top of the list. If this box is unchecked, the topics will stay in their original position (I have this on)<br>
<br>
Language<br>
Choose your desired language for your control center<br>
Posts will still be in the language in which they posted.  Choices are English, French, German, Spanish<br>
<br>
Number of replies per page<br>
