<br>
Use HTML<br>
Checking this box will enable HTML in your posts. We suggest keeping this turned off and using ezCodes instead. (html is turned of for this message board).<br>
<br>
Use Ezcodes<br>
Checking this box will convert EzCodes to equivalent HTML.<br>
<br>
